releases.description:
## Changes
- Spoiler colours are now done via CSS tokens. You can now override the spoiler colours via the following CSS override:

```css
body {
	--inline-spoilers-hidden-foreground: black !important;
	--inline-spoilers-hidden-background: black !important;

	--inline-spoilers-revealed-foreground: white !important;
	--inline-spoilers-revealed-background: black !important;

	--inline-spoilers-spoiler-radius: 0 !important;
}
```

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/logonoff/obsidian-inline-spoilers/compare/1.2.2...1.2.3
